description:
The following does not pass when the source {{Publisher}} emits more than one chunk of data. 

{code:java}
List<ByteBuffer> rawSource = Arrays.asList(ByteBuffer.wrap("first".getBytes()), ByteBuffer.wrap("second".getBytes()));
Publisher<ByteBuffer> source = Publishers.publishAndFlatten(callback -> callback.onResult(rawSource, null));
 
GridFSUploadPublisher<ObjectId> upload = buckets.uploadFromPublisher("chunked.xml", source);

Mono.from(upload)
    .as(StepVerifier::create)
    .expectNextCount(1)
    .verifyComplete();
{code}
